textAfterTable: 9 Songs Biography Formed: 1980 in Auburn, NY Genre: Rock Years Active: '80s, '90s, '00s, '10s One of the most internationally successful bands in all of heavy metaldom, Auburn, New York-born power metal outfit Manowar — Eric Adams (vocals), Karl Logan (guitars), Joey DeMaio (bass), and Donnie Hamzik (drums) — have sold over nine million records since their inception in 1980.
